  "267:275": {
    "inputs": {
      "preview_markdown": "Style: cinematic-realistic. A sleek, black sedan sits stationary on a paved road. The camera slowly pans into the car, very slow, revealing leather seats and a dashboard of chrome buttons. The car then starts up, and you hear the engine—a low rumble that vibrates through the chassis. The car doesn' large-motion or shifts position. Only ambient city sounds and car sounds – subtle hum of tires, click of turn signal—fill the space. Exterior shots reveal the car’s paintwork. Subtle reflections of light play across the hood’s curve. Inside, sunlight streams in through the windshield, illuminating dust motes dancing in the air. The camera continues to pan slowly, taking in the details of the interior—leather upholstery, chrome trim, and wood-paneled dash. Ambient city sounds—distant horns, muffled voices—drift in and out of focus. The camera pauses briefly on the steering wheel, then resumes its slow pan upward, settling on the roof of the car.",
